  replyText:
  - I would hope so. Otherwise, my method acting isn't working.
  - Yes, yes, I am. You going to shame me for being dramatic as well?
  - Oh, I wouldn't say that. I'm just good at crying, that's all.
  - Well, I try to fit whatever needs to be done at the moment.
  - ...Is that a joke?
